    {
        "text": "...and it had hundreds of thousands of employees, mostly in North America.",
        "startTime": 45813,
        "endTime": 49805,
        "slowStartTime": 68869,
        "slowEndTime": 74932
    },
    {
        "text": "Today, there are 20 American companies with more than 90 billion in revenue.",
        "startTime": 50883,
        "endTime": 55025,
        "slowStartTime": 76475,
        "slowEndTime": 82763
    },
    {
        "text": "And many of them like Walmart or GE have half or more of their employees...",
