        "endTime": 59853,
        "slowStartTime": 83429,
        "slowEndTime": 90005
    },
    {
        "text": "...working outside the US.",
        "startTime": 59938,
        "endTime": 61161,
        "slowStartTime": 90057,
        "slowEndTime": 91967
    },
    {
        "text": "If you're at the helm of one of America's most important corporations these days,...",
        "startTime": 61837,
        "endTime": 65379,
        "slowStartTime": 92906,
        "slowEndTime": 98293
    },
    {
        "text": "...you're acting on the world stage.",
        "startTime": 65913,
        "endTime": 67658,
        "slowStartTime": 99020,
        "slowEndTime": 101712
    },
    {
        "text": "It's a bigger job.",
        "startTime": 68268,
        "endTime": 69175,
        "slowStartTime": 102552,
        "slowEndTime": 103987
    },
    {
        "text": "But the second reason CEOs are paid more is that they're paid differently.",
        "startTime": 69936,
        "endTime": 74237,
        "slowStartTime": 105054,
        "slowEndTime": 111581
    },
    {
        "text": "They're more likely to be compensated...",
